ion/index.html">Introduction</a></li></ul></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-9985"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/index.html">I: God, Humanity &#038; Sin</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-7621"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-0-god-created/index.html">1.0 God Created</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10017"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-1-male-and-female/index.html">1.1 Male and Female</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10024"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-2-it-was-very-good/index.html">1.2 It Was Very Good</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10031"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-3-science-vs-the-bible/index.html">1.3 Science vs. the Bible</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10030"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-4-humanity-sin-a-fallen-world-sin-suffering-death-enter/index.html">1.4 Humanity &#038; Sin</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10037"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-5-we-are-all-sinners/index.html">1.5 We Are All Sinners</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10040"><a href="part-i-god-humanity-sin/1-6-the-coming-great-day-of-judgment/index.html">1.6 The Coming Great Day of Judgment</a></li></ul></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-10047"><a href="part-ii-our-hope/index.html">II: Our Hope</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10066"><a href="part-ii-our-hope/2-0-who-is-jesus-of-nazareth/index.html">2.0 Who is Jesus of Nazareth?</a></li><li class="menu-item menu-item-typ